content: Sign up for a training here: https://events.democrats.org/event/672393/. I don't know what you mean regarding the f2 code. You'll have to set that up when we direct message you the info.

I did the text team training last night from 7 to 8 pm. 
As I stated, I believe it’s the same  as GAVIN Newsom‘s text team. I was doing it for weeks and I’m very familiar with the process so what is the next step for me based on this information that I’m giving you?
After you take a training. 24-72 hours after that we'll send you info over a direct message.
